---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Professional Journey | Adesh Gaur"
  description="More than two decades of enterprise engineering, integration architecture, healthcare payer integration, Boomi leadership, and AI solution development."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Page Hero -->
    <section class="page-hero journey-hero">
      <div class="container page-hero-grid">
        <div class="page-hero-content">
          <p class="eyebrow">Professional Journey</p>

          <h1 class="hero-title-wide">
            Two decades of enterprise integration leadership.
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-lead">
            Evolving from application and database engineering into enterprise
            integration architecture, healthcare interoperability, Boomi
            leadership, and AI-powered solutions.
          </p>

          <p class="hero-copy">
            My professional journey has been shaped by complex enterprise
            systems, integration modernization, healthcare payer ecosystems,
            technical leadership, and a continued focus on learning and
            practical innovation.
          </p>

          <div class="button-row">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="#journey-timeline">
              Explore My Journey
            </a>

            <a class="button button-secondary" href="/contact">
              Let&rsquo;s Connect
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside
          class="page-summary-panel journey-summary"
          aria-labelledby="journey-focus-title"
        >
          <p id="journey-focus-title" class="panel-label">
            Career Evolution
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">01</span>

              <div>
                <strong>Enterprise Engineering</strong>
                <small>
                  Java, databases, SQL, applications, and integration
                </small>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">02</span>

              <div>
                <strong>Integration Architecture</strong>
                <small>
                  Middleware, APIs, messaging, patterns, and governance
                </small>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">03</span>

              <div>
                <strong>Healthcare Integration</strong>
                <small>
                  Payer platforms, HIPAA EDI, interoperability, and support
                </small>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">04</span>

              <div>
                <strong>Enterprise AI</strong>
                <small>
                  Agentic AI, RAG, local models, and intelligent automation
                </small>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Career Progression -->
    <section id="journey-timeline" class="section section-muted">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Career Progression</p>

          <h2>
            Building deeper expertise through every stage of the journey.
          </h2>

          <p class="section-intro">
            Each stage of my career has added new technical depth, broader
            delivery responsibility, and stronger domain expertise while
            maintaining a practical focus on enterprise outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline">
          <article class="card timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-heading">
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">01</span>

              <div>
                <span class="timeline-stage">Foundation</span>
                <h3>Application &amp; Database Engineering</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Built a strong foundation in Java, SQL, PL/SQL, databases,
              enterprise applications, data processing, and system integration.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-heading">
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">02</span>

              <div>
                <span class="timeline-stage">Expansion</span>
                <h3>Enterprise Integration</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Expanded into middleware architecture, reusable integration
              patterns, transformation, APIs, asynchronous processing, and
              production reliability.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-heading">
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">03</span>

              <div>
                <span class="timeline-stage">Specialization</span>
                <h3>Boomi Architecture &amp; Leadership</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Led architecture, development, API design, Event Streams,
              estimation, monitoring, governance, reviews, and technical
              delivery using Boomi.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-heading">
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">04</span>

              <div>
                <span class="timeline-stage">Domain Focus</span>
                <h3>Healthcare Integration &amp; EDI</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Specialized in healthcare payer integration involving enrollment,
              claims, remittance, premium payments, HIPAA X12, APIs,
              validation, and operational support.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-heading">
              <span class="marker" aria-hidden="true">05</span>

              <div>
                <span class="timeline-stage">Current Direction</span>
                <h3>AI-powered Enterprise Solutions</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Applying Agentic AI, RAG, deterministic engineering tools, local
              models, and knowledge retrieval to enterprise architecture and
              healthcare integration challenges.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Approach -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Leadership Approach</p>

          <h2>Technical depth supported by delivery responsibility.</h2>

          <p class="section-intro">
            My leadership approach combines architecture, solutioning,
            estimation, technical guidance, operational awareness, and a strong
            focus on reusable and maintainable delivery practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Architecture</h3>

            <p>
              Translate business requirements into scalable integration
              landscapes, patterns, contracts, and operational models.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Solutioning &amp; Estimation</h3>

            <p>
              Support discovery, complexity assessment, assumptions,
              dependencies, delivery planning, and effort estimation.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Technical Leadership</h3>

            <p>
              Guide development teams through reviews, standards, reusable
              practices, troubleshooting, and production readiness.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Closing CTA -->
    <section class="section page-cta">
      <div class="container page-cta-inner">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Professional Opportunities</p>

          <h2>
            Looking for enterprise integration architecture or technical
            leadership expertise?
          </h2>

          <p>
            Connect with me to discuss Boomi, Healthcare Integration &amp; EDI,
            APIs, modernization, architecture, or AI-assisted solutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/contact">
            Start a Conversation
          </a>

          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/credentials">
            View Credentials
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .panel-label {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .section-heading {
    max-width: 880px;
  }

  .section-heading h2 {
    max-width: 24ch;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(18rem, 0.6fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .timeline-heading {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.5rem minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .timeline-heading h3 {
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
  }

  .timeline-stage {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .timeline-card > p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .timeline-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>